## Open source projects

* [MBrace](http://nessos.github.io/MBrace) Distributed computation and Big Data analytics framework.
* [FsPickler](http://nessos.github.io/FsPickler) Fast, General-purpose serializer for the .NET framework.
* [LinqOptimizer](http://nessos.github.io/LinqOptimizer) An automatic query optimizer for LINQ to Objects and PLINQ.
